channel.title: Comments on: Irish company WRI brings Boo.com comes back from the dead

item.title: By: DUBLIN.net
item.dc:creator: DUBLIN.net
item.description: I'd love to know which pairs of hands it passed through (and how much) before ending up with WRI. From what little I know about the domain aftermarket, three letter dotcoms are pretty pricey(?), but the coverage alone (and the resulting link love) might have been worth it.
